WEBVTT

00:23.830 --> 00:25.030
Something happened.

00:25.640 --> 00:27.030
I just heard the news outside

00:27.030 --> 00:29.350
that Qingshan Manor intercepted and killed
His Majesty outside Zhenhuangcheng.

00:29.350 --> 00:31.120
Yan Xun died at the hands of Zhuge Yue.

00:31.120 --> 00:32.560
Where did you get this news?

00:32.560 --> 00:33.690
Did you see the body?

00:34.390 --> 00:35.590
I didn't see the body.

00:35.960 --> 00:37.470
But all night, several teams

00:37.470 --> 00:39.750
of Qingshan Manor spies
were rushing in and out of the city.

00:39.750 --> 00:41.880
It doesn't seem to be a baseless rumor.

00:42.030 --> 00:43.090
I don't believe it.

00:44.150 --> 00:45.550
Without seeing the body,

00:45.960 --> 00:47.690
I won't believe Yan Xun is dead.

00:54.430 --> 00:57.000
Yan Xun, the King of Great Yan,
attempted to escape

00:57.000 --> 00:58.110
and fell off a cliff to his death!

00:58.110 --> 00:59.110
He's dead?

01:00.710 --> 01:02.710
I heard the King of Great Yan
was incredibly brave.

01:02.710 --> 01:04.640
Qingshan Manor is truly formidable.

01:02.990 --> 01:04.030
[Notice from Zhenhuangcheng]

01:05.480 --> 01:07.540
Yan Xun's body hasn't been found yet.

01:15.920 --> 01:17.650
Great Yan's General Cheng Yuan

01:17.680 --> 01:19.000
has been executed.

01:19.150 --> 01:20.120
Good! Good!

01:20.120 --> 01:22.150
-Good! Good!
-Good! Good!

01:22.150 --> 01:23.280
It's General Cheng.

01:26.350 --> 01:28.120
We can't let Cheng Yuan's body

01:28.430 --> 01:30.289
fall into the hands of Great Yong.

02:09.120 --> 02:11.550
[Tomb of General Cheng Yuan]

02:10.310 --> 02:11.640
You don't need to worry.

02:12.150 --> 02:14.240
Since they haven't found Yan Xun's body,

02:14.240 --> 02:16.100
it means he should still be alive.

02:16.910 --> 02:18.240
As long as he is alive,

02:18.960 --> 02:21.160
he will definitely return to Great Yan.

02:29.800 --> 02:30.710
General Cheng,

02:31.030 --> 02:33.590
I didn't expect that
after being enemies for so many years,

02:33.590 --> 02:35.960
I would be the one to bury you.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.260
General Cheng,

02:42.360 --> 02:43.560
if there is a next life

02:44.360 --> 02:46.490
and we are both born in Great Yan again,

02:47.470 --> 02:48.630
let us be comrades

02:49.520 --> 02:51.320
and protect Great Yan together.

04:17.500 --> 04:22.690
[REBIRTH]

04:23.340 --> 04:25.640
[Episode 37]

04:40.270 --> 04:41.070
Young Master.

04:51.190 --> 04:54.070
The troops of Great Yong
have reached Zhutancheng.

04:54.920 --> 04:58.120
In a few days,
they will reach the Ximeng border.

05:00.480 --> 05:01.280
Young Master.

05:01.830 --> 05:02.630
There is one thing

05:02.630 --> 05:04.030
that I don't understand.

05:05.390 --> 05:06.000
Speak.

05:07.510 --> 05:09.000
His Highness and you

05:09.000 --> 05:11.510
have always been friends
through life and death.

05:11.510 --> 05:13.430
After Muhe Lie and Wei Guang died,

05:13.800 --> 05:15.430
something also happened to the Mu family.

05:15.430 --> 05:17.890
But why did he give
most of the military power

05:18.040 --> 05:20.270
to the Prince of Jing,
who has always stayed away from the court?

05:20.270 --> 05:23.360
The Crown Prince is no longer
the Seventh Prince he used to be.

05:23.360 --> 05:25.360
He is the Crown Prince of Great Yong.

05:25.430 --> 05:26.800
As the Crown Prince,

05:27.680 --> 05:29.940
he will no longer be friends with anyone.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.530
But if that's the case,

05:33.480 --> 05:36.409
why did you still choose
to support the Crown Prince?

05:54.159 --> 05:54.960
Castor beans.

05:55.680 --> 05:57.159
They cause shortness of breath.

05:57.159 --> 05:58.070
Within 2 hours,

05:59.120 --> 06:00.520
one dies of suffocation.

06:01.050 --> 06:04.670
♪ The dust in the world ♪

06:05.070 --> 06:08.550
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

06:09.370 --> 06:12.170
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

06:12.000 --> 06:12.860
Qianji Poison.

06:13.000 --> 06:14.350
♪ And not be scared? ♪

06:14.240 --> 06:15.680
It causes the poisoned
to convulse all over

06:14.380 --> 06:16.390
♪ A slight ripple ♪

06:15.950 --> 06:17.240
and die bleeding from all orifices.

06:16.570 --> 06:20.170
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

06:17.480 --> 06:18.880
You have one more chance.

06:20.450 --> 06:23.820
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

06:24.790 --> 06:27.630
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

06:28.290 --> 06:31.670
♪ Let it be ♪

06:32.750 --> 06:36.180
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

06:36.650 --> 06:39.670
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

06:40.040 --> 06:41.680
♪ Go weaving ♪

06:42.000 --> 06:46.960
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

06:45.720 --> 06:46.780
It is the upas tree,

06:47.000 --> 06:48.240
also known as "Instant Death."

06:48.090 --> 06:50.640
♪ We face ♪

06:48.750 --> 06:49.810
It is highly toxic.

06:50.040 --> 06:52.600
If it enters the heart, there is no cure.

06:50.659 --> 06:54.510
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

06:53.190 --> 06:54.920
You are a spy of Qingshan Manor.

06:55.430 --> 06:57.830
Teaching you to identify poisonous plants
is for taking others' lives,

06:55.670 --> 06:58.400
♪ Even in extreme pain ♪

06:57.830 --> 06:58.950
not poisoning yourself.

06:58.430 --> 07:03.190
♪ We don't even wince ♪

06:59.720 --> 07:00.720
In today's test,

07:01.750 --> 07:02.720
you failed.

07:03.220 --> 07:06.240
♪ Why in this world ♪

07:04.720 --> 07:05.850
I know martial arts.

07:05.950 --> 07:07.870
Why can't I kill them openly,

07:06.260 --> 07:10.670
♪ The staunchest heart
and strongest soul ♪

07:08.870 --> 07:10.720
instead of using vicious methods?

07:10.720 --> 07:11.800
The rules of this world

07:11.650 --> 07:17.890
♪ Yield so easily to gentle warmth? ♪

07:12.310 --> 07:14.510
won't care about your ways and methods.

07:15.120 --> 07:16.720
You can only use any means necessary

07:16.720 --> 07:17.720
to survive.

07:18.640 --> 07:21.430
♪ We once beheld ♪

07:19.560 --> 07:21.460
Then the rules of this world are wrong.

07:21.460 --> 07:24.860
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

07:24.560 --> 07:25.950
Don't you think so?

07:26.560 --> 07:27.830
Whether it is you or me,

07:26.580 --> 07:29.220
♪ Beauty never ♪

07:28.560 --> 07:30.000
if we can't change anything,

07:29.250 --> 07:33.980
♪ Lasts for long ♪

07:30.560 --> 07:33.020
we're not qualified
to judge right or wrong.

07:33.560 --> 07:35.000
The first thing you have to do now

07:34.250 --> 07:37.770
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

07:35.870 --> 07:37.920
is to survive in this world.

07:37.790 --> 07:42.230
♪ It's just a stone ♪

07:42.530 --> 07:49.740
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

07:45.159 --> 07:45.830
Because

07:47.190 --> 07:48.240
I have no choice.

07:50.550 --> 08:01.530
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

08:15.310 --> 08:15.920
Eat.

08:31.600 --> 08:33.440
Go to hell!

08:37.799 --> 08:38.740
Don't kill me! Don't kill me!

08:38.740 --> 08:40.539
I'll tell you Zhao Che's secret!

08:40.549 --> 08:42.200
Didn't you say you knew nothing?

08:42.200 --> 08:43.080
I know! I know!

08:43.100 --> 08:44.270
I will tell you

08:44.320 --> 08:45.380
everything I know.

08:45.750 --> 08:47.000
Then speak out.

08:47.150 --> 08:49.010
Let's see if it's worth your life.

08:49.270 --> 08:51.600
The third prophecy Jia Meng will announce

08:51.600 --> 08:53.390
is that the Faceless God Sect
will use the sacred fire

08:53.390 --> 08:55.590
to burn the current Chosen One to death,

08:55.720 --> 08:58.050
which will be replaced
by a new Chosen One.

08:58.150 --> 09:00.080
This is all Zhao Che's conspiracy.

09:00.480 --> 09:01.630
The person to die

09:02.440 --> 09:03.840
is the current Emperor.

09:07.000 --> 09:09.400
How can you prove
you are telling the truth?

09:10.910 --> 09:12.550
Following Zhao Che's secret order,

09:12.550 --> 09:14.080
in the ancestral temple
of Tianyuan Palace,

09:14.080 --> 09:16.440
I hid a large amount of
spontaneously combustible flint powder.

09:16.440 --> 09:18.910
This is the evidence of his plot
to murder His Majesty!

09:18.910 --> 09:20.000
Because in 2 months,

09:20.000 --> 09:21.840
it'll be His Majesty's birthday.

09:21.840 --> 09:23.390
Under the guise
of renovating the ancestral temple

09:23.390 --> 09:25.080
to celebrate His Majesty's birthday,

09:25.080 --> 09:26.270
Zhao Che has long replaced the guards

09:26.270 --> 09:28.000
with his own people.

09:29.360 --> 09:30.550
If you don't believe me,

09:30.550 --> 09:31.870
you can check the records

09:31.870 --> 09:34.800
of the grain carts I dispatched
in and out of the city.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.000
Those grain carts

09:36.550 --> 09:38.410
were specially used to transport

09:38.510 --> 09:39.960
flint powder for him!

10:05.360 --> 10:06.630
According to Mu Shen,

10:07.510 --> 10:10.000
there is a secret room
in the ancestral temple.

10:10.000 --> 10:11.600
Following Zhao Che's order,

10:12.000 --> 10:14.750
he hid the flint powder
in the secret room.

10:15.600 --> 10:17.150
So on the day of the birthday,

10:17.150 --> 10:18.440
the flint powder
will spontaneously ignite,

10:18.440 --> 10:20.770
and the ancestral temple will catch fire.

10:20.840 --> 10:22.480
Zhao Che is using this cult

10:22.480 --> 10:23.940
to eliminate dissidents.

10:24.240 --> 10:25.550
The followers of the Faceless God Sect

10:25.550 --> 10:27.720
have already begun to slaughter civilians

10:27.720 --> 10:30.150
who refuse to join the sect
outside Zhenhuangcheng.

10:30.150 --> 10:32.550
These are all secretly ordered
by Zhao Che.

10:33.600 --> 10:34.200
But now,

10:34.200 --> 10:36.550
we can't even get close to
Tianyuan Palace,

10:36.550 --> 10:38.720
let alone enter the ancestral temple.

10:40.480 --> 10:41.440
I have an idea.

10:45.150 --> 10:46.480
Generals and soldiers,

10:47.240 --> 10:49.370
the Faceless God has punished Ximeng.

10:49.720 --> 10:51.200
The continuous floods in Ximeng

10:51.200 --> 10:53.080
can't wash away its sins.

10:53.440 --> 10:54.440
We are going there

10:54.790 --> 10:57.750
to redeem this sinful land
for the Faceless God

10:58.150 --> 11:00.480
and bring the glory and light
of Great Yong

11:00.720 --> 11:03.720
to Ximeng and its people.

11:04.270 --> 11:05.030
From now on,

11:05.720 --> 11:08.150
Ximeng will become part of Great Yong!

11:08.360 --> 11:09.910
-Annex Ximeng!
-Annex Ximeng!

11:09.910 --> 11:11.480
-Annex Ximeng!
-Annex Ximeng!

11:11.480 --> 11:13.210
-Annex Ximeng!
-Annex Ximeng!

11:15.670 --> 11:16.360
Wait!

11:25.320 --> 11:27.450
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty,

11:27.550 --> 11:28.960
Your Highness.

11:32.200 --> 11:34.870
General Xing Le,
you've been on sick leave for days.

11:34.870 --> 11:36.670
Why do you suddenly appear today

11:37.120 --> 11:39.720
and hinder the army
from setting off to Ximeng?

11:40.670 --> 11:42.000
What's your intention?

11:42.480 --> 11:43.280
Your Majesty,

11:43.750 --> 11:45.270
I was not on sick leave.

11:45.630 --> 11:48.430
I was just assassinated
in my mansion a few days ago

11:48.750 --> 11:49.870
and forced to flee.

11:50.320 --> 11:51.910
That's why I went missing.

11:52.480 --> 11:54.210
As for the news of my sick leave,

11:54.600 --> 11:56.960
I don't know where it came from.

11:58.270 --> 11:59.550
I was assassinated

11:59.870 --> 12:01.800
and fortunately saved by someone.

12:01.870 --> 12:04.240
I've also brought
this person here to meet you.

12:04.240 --> 12:07.040
She also has something important
to report to you.

12:07.600 --> 12:08.550
Who is it?

12:09.510 --> 12:10.970
Finish your words at once.

12:40.200 --> 12:40.840
Guards!

12:41.240 --> 12:42.150
Protect His Majesty!

12:42.150 --> 12:43.510
Capture the assassin Chu Qiao!

12:43.510 --> 12:44.750
Wait, Your Highness!

12:45.270 --> 12:46.330
Please hear me out!

12:46.580 --> 12:48.300
Chu Qiao is here to surrender!

12:50.720 --> 12:52.630
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty,

12:52.630 --> 12:55.120
Your Highness.

12:56.550 --> 12:57.670
I, Chu Qiao,

12:58.480 --> 13:00.240
carrying the names of Queen Ximeng

13:00.240 --> 13:02.360
and Empress Dowager Xiuli of Biantang,

13:02.360 --> 13:04.690
have come specially to Father and Brother

13:05.030 --> 13:05.910
to surrender.

13:06.750 --> 13:08.110
Why are you just standing there?

13:08.110 --> 13:10.240
This person is a guilty slave
who defected from Great Yong

13:10.240 --> 13:12.550
and once assassinated
the Thirteenth Prince.

13:12.550 --> 13:14.210
Don't listen to her nonsense.

13:14.360 --> 13:15.490
Kill her on the spot.

13:15.510 --> 13:16.550
I will reward you heavily.

13:16.550 --> 13:17.240
Wait.

13:31.790 --> 13:32.670
Chu Qiao,

13:34.030 --> 13:34.960
I recognize you.

13:35.960 --> 13:37.560
In the 23rd year of Tianqian,

13:37.600 --> 13:41.000
I appointed you as the imperial guard's
martial arts instructor.

13:41.000 --> 13:41.750
At that time,

13:42.910 --> 13:44.720
you were still with Yan Xun.

13:47.270 --> 13:48.360
Just now,

13:49.630 --> 13:51.630
what did you call yourself?

13:54.240 --> 13:55.100
Your daughter.

13:59.550 --> 14:01.630
I pay my respects to you, Father.

14:04.790 --> 14:05.650
Half a year ago,

14:06.200 --> 14:07.840
you sent an envoy of Great Yong,

14:07.840 --> 14:09.910
Lord Zhuge Muqing, to Ximeng

14:10.270 --> 14:12.360
to confer the title
of Princess Ximeng on me,

14:12.360 --> 14:14.270
claiming that I was your lost daughter.

14:14.270 --> 14:16.370
At that time, I was momentarily confused

14:16.370 --> 14:17.900
and refused your kindness,

14:18.000 --> 14:20.000
failing to accept the decree
and acknowledge my ancestry in time.

14:20.000 --> 14:22.510
Now I feel deeply regretful,

14:23.200 --> 14:25.390
so I came specially to you

14:26.360 --> 14:27.620
to apologize, Father.

14:35.750 --> 14:38.120
We sent people all the way to Biantang

14:38.120 --> 14:40.450
to inform General Sun to save General Chu.

14:40.480 --> 14:41.540
But what happened?

14:41.670 --> 14:43.390
Great Yong didn't care at all.

14:43.550 --> 14:45.630
The Biantang envoys
were killed in Zhenhuangcheng.

14:45.630 --> 14:47.200
We don't even know whether General Chu

14:47.200 --> 14:48.130
is dead or alive.

14:49.870 --> 14:51.720
The situation in Great Yong has changed.

14:51.720 --> 14:52.780
What else can we do?

14:53.750 --> 14:55.770
The Xiuli Army only has a few hundred men.

14:55.770 --> 14:57.670
Even with all the soldiers of Ximeng,

14:57.670 --> 14:59.330
it's just a drop in the bucket.

15:04.080 --> 15:05.320
What about the others?

15:05.320 --> 15:06.720
Do you all think so too?

15:08.390 --> 15:09.190
Commander He,

15:09.790 --> 15:10.650
over the years,

15:10.870 --> 15:11.750
we've seen too many heroes

15:11.750 --> 15:13.360
who fought to the death.

15:14.200 --> 15:15.600
No bodies were left.

15:15.960 --> 15:17.200
Not even a grave

15:17.200 --> 15:18.510
or a name was left.

15:19.320 --> 15:20.720
We only have these people.

15:20.720 --> 15:21.920
If we go to Great Yong,

15:23.000 --> 15:24.840
you know better than us the outcome

15:24.840 --> 15:26.030
of kicking against the pricks.

15:26.030 --> 15:27.760
We're indebted to General Chu!

15:28.550 --> 15:29.840
Without her,

15:29.840 --> 15:31.900
we would have died in the wilderness!

15:32.910 --> 15:35.240
Now that General Chu's life
is on the line,

15:35.630 --> 15:37.760
are we going to stand by and do nothing?

15:42.670 --> 15:43.470
Commander He,

15:44.120 --> 15:45.120
for so many years,

15:45.510 --> 15:47.770
hasn't the Xiuli Army shed enough blood?

15:49.030 --> 15:50.510
General Chu indeed saved us,

15:50.510 --> 15:51.200
but we...

15:52.960 --> 15:53.840
but we also have to survive

15:53.840 --> 15:55.750
for the sake of our families.

15:56.200 --> 15:57.360
I got married in Biantang.

15:57.360 --> 15:58.600
My wife is about to give birth.

15:58.600 --> 16:00.240
I don't want my child to be born

16:00.240 --> 16:01.320
without a father.

16:02.600 --> 16:04.660
We are all brothers of the Xiuli Army.

16:04.750 --> 16:07.080
None of us here
owes General Chu our lives,

16:07.080 --> 16:09.030
nor do we owe the Xiuli Army anything.

16:09.030 --> 16:10.560
I have no right to force you.

16:10.670 --> 16:11.930
I respect your choice.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.150
But I

16:14.440 --> 16:16.040
still have to take this path.

16:28.750 --> 16:29.840
Father,

16:30.670 --> 16:32.470
if you forgive my past mistakes,

16:32.670 --> 16:35.440
the people of Ximeng and I

16:35.960 --> 16:38.200
will submit to you.

16:39.630 --> 16:40.320
Chu Qiao,

16:41.240 --> 16:43.700
you're a runaway slave
from Qingshan Manor.

16:44.000 --> 16:47.000
You and Heir Apparent Yan Xun
defected from Great Yong

16:47.000 --> 16:49.060
and bathed Zhenhuangcheng in blood.

16:49.550 --> 16:50.870
Now you dare to pretend to be a princess—

16:50.870 --> 16:52.600
Whether I'm a runaway slave
from Qingshan Manor

16:52.600 --> 16:55.130
or Father's daughter
left in Qingshan Manor,

16:56.120 --> 16:57.380
it's not for you to say.

16:58.910 --> 17:01.960
Father's edict has already made it clear.

17:02.960 --> 17:05.690
On the day Lord Zhuge Muqing
announced the edict,

17:06.240 --> 17:08.200
Young Master Zhuge, you were also present,

17:08.200 --> 17:08.930
weren't you?

17:12.240 --> 17:13.109
Last time at Ximeng Pass—

17:13.109 --> 17:13.720
Enough.

17:16.829 --> 17:17.720
Say no more.

17:19.880 --> 17:20.589
Chu Qiao,

17:21.109 --> 17:22.510
I only have one question.

17:22.720 --> 17:24.480
Why should I believe

17:26.030 --> 17:27.760
that you sincerely surrender?

17:28.200 --> 17:28.830
Father,

17:29.270 --> 17:31.070
Great Yong is rich and powerful.

17:31.200 --> 17:32.000
But Ximeng

17:32.400 --> 17:33.920
is just a barren land.

17:34.790 --> 17:37.400
Now that it has been punished
by the Faceless God,

17:37.400 --> 17:39.160
if I remain obstinate,

17:39.480 --> 17:41.350
it will only make Ximeng suffer.

17:42.310 --> 17:45.270
But if I lead Ximeng
to submit to Great Yong,

17:45.400 --> 17:47.720
it can prevent a war
between the two armies,

17:47.720 --> 17:50.000
and wealth and glory will await me.

17:50.480 --> 17:52.610
Why would I make an enemy of Great Yong?

17:54.920 --> 17:55.750
Besides,

17:56.070 --> 17:58.880
Father, you are a hundred times wiser
than I am.

17:59.350 --> 18:00.160
I believe

18:00.440 --> 18:02.440
you know better than I do

18:02.830 --> 18:05.230
that having an extra princess
in Great Yong

18:05.550 --> 18:08.240
is better than having an extra enemy.

18:11.350 --> 18:12.150
Your Majesty,

18:12.680 --> 18:15.410
what Chu Qiao said
is not entirely unreasonable.

18:15.680 --> 18:18.810
If Ximeng could submit to Great Yong
without bloodshed,

18:19.240 --> 18:21.240
it would be a great blessing indeed.

18:22.240 --> 18:23.680
If we continue to doubt her,

18:23.680 --> 18:25.540
we might miss a good opportunity.

18:30.510 --> 18:31.310
Your Majesty,

18:32.110 --> 18:33.200
I know

18:33.200 --> 18:34.260
Chu Qiao very much.

18:34.830 --> 18:35.830
In my opinion,

18:36.270 --> 18:37.440
her loyalty

18:38.000 --> 18:39.270
is not necessarily true.

18:39.270 --> 18:41.830
What are you talking about,
Young Master Zhuge?

18:41.830 --> 18:43.440
If you can forsake the darkness
for the light,

18:43.440 --> 18:44.510
betray Ximeng,

18:44.720 --> 18:46.780
and pledge allegiance to Great Yong,

18:46.960 --> 18:49.590
why can't I?

18:52.830 --> 18:53.480
Father.

18:54.400 --> 18:55.750
If you have any doubts,

18:56.030 --> 18:57.640
after I enter the ancestral temple
of Great Yong

18:57.640 --> 18:58.960
and my name is added
to the imperial genealogy

18:58.960 --> 19:00.440
as a princess,

19:00.440 --> 19:03.440
I will personally hand over
Ximeng's jade seal, military tally,

19:03.440 --> 19:04.840
and letter of submission

19:05.240 --> 19:07.070
to you.

19:07.790 --> 19:10.650
At that time, Father,
you just need to give the order

19:10.830 --> 19:12.720
to send the Yong Army
stationed outside Ximeng Pass

19:12.720 --> 19:14.310
to Ximeng Pass.

19:14.750 --> 19:15.750
By then,

19:16.590 --> 19:19.510
Ximeng will become Great Yong's territory.

19:20.680 --> 19:22.610
If you enter the ancestral temple,

19:22.960 --> 19:25.000
have your name added to the genealogy,

19:25.000 --> 19:27.000
but immediately go back on your word,

19:27.000 --> 19:28.110
what then?

19:28.640 --> 19:29.440
Unless

19:30.310 --> 19:33.170
you hand over
Ximeng's jade seal and military tally

19:33.680 --> 19:34.830
first.

19:35.240 --> 19:35.830
Fine.

19:38.240 --> 19:38.790
But

19:39.590 --> 19:40.790
I have a request.

19:41.310 --> 19:43.110
Please issue a decree immediately,

19:43.110 --> 19:45.510
granting me my rightful title of Princess.

19:46.640 --> 19:47.510
In 3 days,

19:48.030 --> 19:50.030
I will be in front of Tianyuan Palace

19:50.310 --> 19:52.770
to hand over
the military tally and jade seal

19:52.920 --> 19:54.590
to you, Father,

19:54.750 --> 19:57.590
and sign Ximeng's letter of submission
to Great Yong,

19:57.590 --> 19:59.390
witnessed by all the officials.

19:59.550 --> 20:00.240
After that,

20:00.480 --> 20:03.540
please let me worship
at the ancestral temple directly

20:03.550 --> 20:05.280
and add my name to the genealogy

20:05.400 --> 20:06.640
to show sincerity.

20:07.720 --> 20:09.590
Are you bargaining with me?

20:09.960 --> 20:13.310
You worry that I'll go back on my word
after entering the genealogy.

20:13.310 --> 20:14.770
I am naturally also afraid

20:15.030 --> 20:16.890
that after getting the jade seal,

20:16.920 --> 20:19.980
you'll go back on your word
and deny me as your daughter.

20:23.270 --> 20:24.200
Stand up.

20:32.310 --> 20:33.000
Fine.

20:33.880 --> 20:34.680
I

20:36.030 --> 20:36.880
promise you.

20:37.750 --> 20:39.830
Thank you, Father.

21:40.200 --> 21:40.960
Father.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.530
You come with a sword

21:47.240 --> 21:48.480
and armor,

21:49.240 --> 21:50.840
barging into my bedchamber.

21:52.240 --> 21:54.300
Are you forcing me to abdicate again?

21:54.960 --> 21:56.090
I don't understand.

21:56.880 --> 21:59.240
Why did you agree to Chu Qiao?

21:59.960 --> 22:00.750
Our army

22:00.750 --> 22:03.410
is massed outside Zhenhuangcheng,
ready to go.

22:04.070 --> 22:06.880
We can reach Ximeng in a few months.

22:07.680 --> 22:09.640
A barbarian land like Ximeng

22:10.000 --> 22:11.960
lacks generals and tactics

22:12.110 --> 22:14.040
and has suffered days of flooding.

22:14.200 --> 22:16.200
Our army will surely

22:16.200 --> 22:17.200
be invincible.

22:18.270 --> 22:20.330
Why must we compromise with Chu Qiao?

22:23.830 --> 22:24.790
Besides,

22:25.480 --> 22:27.010
Chu Qiao being the Princess

22:27.020 --> 22:28.870
was just a scheme we made up.

22:29.440 --> 22:31.070
She is no princess at all.

22:31.720 --> 22:33.750
How could such an absurd title

22:33.920 --> 22:34.750
become an excuse

22:34.750 --> 22:36.480
for them to manipulate us?

22:37.720 --> 22:39.830
Our enemy is not Ximeng.

22:40.200 --> 22:42.590
Ximeng is just a barbarian land.

22:43.480 --> 22:44.960
For years past,

22:45.030 --> 22:47.110
we never sought to conquer it.

22:48.350 --> 22:51.000
It would be quite easy
for us to take Ximeng.

22:51.350 --> 22:53.270
But what if Great Yan
takes the opportunity

22:53.270 --> 22:54.680
to march south?

22:55.720 --> 22:57.650
Chu Qiao is not an ordinary person.

22:58.480 --> 23:00.740
She won't submit to Great Yong so easily.

23:00.790 --> 23:02.650
She must have an ulterior motive.

23:06.750 --> 23:08.110
In this world,

23:08.590 --> 23:11.310
no one is without an ulterior motive.

23:11.550 --> 23:13.550
I know there are risks,

23:14.350 --> 23:17.880
but to take Ximeng
without losing a single soldier,

23:18.590 --> 23:21.200
the benefits outweigh the risks.

23:29.720 --> 23:30.550
Che.

23:30.830 --> 23:32.680
Your character is too rigid.

23:34.030 --> 23:36.430
You don't have to be so tough
on some things.

23:37.830 --> 23:38.830
Taking a step back

23:39.880 --> 23:42.200
can help you gain more.

23:50.440 --> 23:51.790
Go to that cabinet.

24:04.590 --> 24:05.480
Inside.

24:06.200 --> 24:07.930
There is a hidden compartment.

24:22.240 --> 24:24.640
That day, you came aggressively,

24:24.640 --> 24:27.570
making me write an edict
to make you the Crown Prince.

24:27.590 --> 24:30.030
I was not coerced by you,

24:30.790 --> 24:32.190
but rather, I had written

24:32.830 --> 24:34.720
this edict long ago.

24:49.790 --> 24:51.110
I doted on Yang

24:51.440 --> 24:53.440
and indulged his reckless behavior

24:53.830 --> 24:56.880
because I never placed great hopes on him.

24:57.590 --> 24:59.200
He was a simple child.

24:59.640 --> 25:00.590
I favored him,

25:01.110 --> 25:02.350
but that doesn't mean

25:02.350 --> 25:04.640
I would hand over Great Yong to him.

25:05.750 --> 25:06.750
In my heart,

25:07.510 --> 25:08.160
you are

25:08.790 --> 25:12.120
the Prince capable of
taking on this great responsibility.

25:16.640 --> 25:17.440
Che.

25:18.920 --> 25:20.400
As a father,

25:21.070 --> 25:23.400
I have failed you in many ways.

25:24.920 --> 25:26.450
I haven't loved you enough,

25:27.590 --> 25:29.110
nor cared for you enough.

25:29.640 --> 25:30.790
But that is because

25:31.350 --> 25:33.640
those are what an ordinary father

25:34.030 --> 25:36.160
should do for his son.

25:36.920 --> 25:38.720
To me, you are

25:39.200 --> 25:40.480
my son,

25:41.480 --> 25:44.340
but more importantly,
the successor of Great Yong.

25:44.830 --> 25:46.830
Now I am old.

25:47.440 --> 25:48.480
I have nothing

25:48.680 --> 25:51.340
but full entrustment and expectations
for you.

25:54.310 --> 25:55.480
I hope

25:56.550 --> 25:59.400
you can guard this foundation
of Great Yong.

26:00.310 --> 26:01.920
I promised Chu Qiao

26:02.440 --> 26:04.640
not only to build up strength
for Great Yong

26:04.640 --> 26:06.700
but also to accumulate power for you.

26:07.400 --> 26:09.400
I believe in the future,

26:10.070 --> 26:11.530
if you achieve something,

26:12.070 --> 26:15.680
you will definitely become
the overlord of this world.

27:06.750 --> 27:07.550
Your Majesty!

27:08.270 --> 27:09.070
Your Majesty!

27:10.070 --> 27:10.870
Your Majesty.

27:11.160 --> 27:12.240
Are you alright?

27:12.750 --> 27:13.680
It's fine.

27:15.000 --> 27:16.030
He believed it.

27:18.680 --> 27:19.480
Your Majesty.

27:20.000 --> 27:22.460
Fortunately, the edict was prepared early.

27:22.590 --> 27:23.550
Otherwise today...

27:23.550 --> 27:24.920
This son of mine

27:26.640 --> 27:29.510
is too much like me when I was young.

27:32.070 --> 27:33.440
He is

27:34.750 --> 27:35.720
more ruthless

27:37.160 --> 27:38.680
and more decisive.

28:48.110 --> 28:48.910
Your Majesty,

28:49.640 --> 28:50.570
why are you here?

29:03.310 --> 29:04.200
What is this?

29:05.310 --> 29:06.440
I don't understand.

29:18.510 --> 29:19.350
I'm sorry.

29:21.480 --> 29:23.030
I failed to bring him back.

29:26.480 --> 29:27.280
Your Majesty.

29:30.030 --> 29:32.290
What are you saying? I don't understand.

29:32.790 --> 29:34.270
This red jade pendant

29:35.680 --> 29:37.280
is your personal belonging.

29:39.240 --> 29:40.100
I recognize it.

29:41.290 --> 29:42.960
He hid it in a secret pocket

29:43.440 --> 29:45.200
and left it to me

29:45.680 --> 29:46.810
with his last words.

29:50.480 --> 29:51.590
I brought it back

29:54.590 --> 29:55.650
to return it to you.

30:05.680 --> 30:07.640
No, I don't want it.

30:08.550 --> 30:09.350
You lied to me.

30:10.310 --> 30:11.570
He can't possibly die.

30:11.750 --> 30:12.750
He promised me

30:13.240 --> 30:14.770
he would come back to see me.

30:17.480 --> 30:18.240
Helian!

30:18.240 --> 30:19.440
Don't touch me!

31:55.270 --> 31:57.880
According to the will of Heaven,

31:58.510 --> 32:01.110
my daughter, Chu Qiao,
is both loyal and brave,

32:01.110 --> 32:02.310
and highly virtuous.

32:02.830 --> 32:05.350
To follow the will of Heaven
and the people,

32:05.880 --> 32:09.140
I hereby confer upon Chu Qiao
the title of Princess Ximeng.

32:09.270 --> 32:11.110
May this title serve as a reward

32:11.640 --> 32:13.200
and show my favor.

32:15.830 --> 32:16.890
Accept the decree.

32:21.240 --> 32:23.030
Thank you, Your Majesty.

32:27.070 --> 32:27.670
Princess,

32:28.440 --> 32:29.270
please wait.

32:40.960 --> 32:43.090
Lord Zhuge, since you invited me here,

32:43.440 --> 32:46.300
it couldn't just be to drink tea
and catch up, right?

32:52.400 --> 32:54.960
Great Yong has more rain than Ximeng.

32:56.000 --> 32:58.880
Although laurel can bloom here,

33:00.070 --> 33:02.000
it doesn't grow as well as in Ximeng.

33:02.000 --> 33:04.590
Ximeng is a place isolated from the world.

33:05.000 --> 33:06.920
Whether it's people or trees,

33:07.240 --> 33:08.680
they can grow freely.

33:08.880 --> 33:10.880
But Ximeng has limited conditions.

33:11.440 --> 33:13.100
It only has sunlight and land,

33:14.030 --> 33:17.270
but no wealth, fine clothes, or rich food.

33:21.790 --> 33:23.720
Everyone has their own ambitions.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.640
Trees too.

33:26.920 --> 33:29.350
Don't force them too much, My Lord.

33:30.240 --> 33:30.960
Xing.

33:33.310 --> 33:34.160
I know why you wanted

33:34.160 --> 33:36.510
to be conferred this title
of Princess Ximeng.

33:36.510 --> 33:38.440
But this is Great Yong's business.

33:38.720 --> 33:40.310
I don't want you involved.

33:40.310 --> 33:41.370
You know very well,

33:41.440 --> 33:43.040
if Zhao Che takes the throne,

33:43.070 --> 33:44.440
Ximeng and Great Yan

33:44.440 --> 33:45.510
will have no peace.

33:49.030 --> 33:51.290
Lord Zhuge, returning to Qingshan Manor

33:51.350 --> 33:52.480
was your choice.

33:53.240 --> 33:54.440
I can't agree with it,

33:55.160 --> 33:56.400
nor will I stop you.

33:57.920 --> 33:59.380
I also ask you, Lord Zhuge,

33:59.960 --> 34:01.560
not to stand in my way either.

34:22.040 --> 34:24.250
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

34:22.090 --> 34:22.920
This sword

34:24.230 --> 34:26.190
was given to me by you, Lord Zhuge.

34:24.370 --> 34:26.909
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

34:26.670 --> 34:27.480
Now,

34:27.340 --> 34:28.639
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

34:28.670 --> 34:30.130
♪ My longing surges ♪

34:28.710 --> 34:30.040
I'm returning it to you.

34:30.150 --> 34:32.659
♪ I become haggard ♪

34:33.270 --> 34:35.719
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

34:35.760 --> 34:38.580
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

34:36.960 --> 34:37.710
Xing.

34:38.600 --> 34:40.300
♪ My love remains ♪

34:40.380 --> 34:43.659
♪ But you're already gone ♪

34:43.699 --> 34:45.090
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

34:45.120 --> 34:47.370
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

34:47.389 --> 34:49.840
♪ How do we start over? ♪

34:49.860 --> 34:53.120
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

34:53.190 --> 34:54.230
I am now

34:53.199 --> 34:55.449
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

34:55.150 --> 34:56.550
Princess Ximeng.

34:55.480 --> 34:58.890
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

34:57.800 --> 34:58.600
In the future,

34:58.910 --> 35:01.230
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

34:59.400 --> 35:00.960
we shouldn't meet again.

35:01.250 --> 35:04.130
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

35:01.550 --> 35:02.710
Lord Zhuge,

35:04.160 --> 35:08.700
♪ In the end ♪

35:04.510 --> 35:06.710
please conduct yourself with dignity.

35:24.550 --> 35:26.630
I know you're definitely
going to save General Chu.

35:26.630 --> 35:27.590
I'll go with you.

35:28.710 --> 35:30.640
You might not come back if you do so.

35:32.320 --> 35:33.150
Who can finish

35:33.710 --> 35:35.970
the entire journey of life alive anyway?

35:50.360 --> 35:52.930
♪ Facing the wind, I tread through frost ♪

35:52.950 --> 35:56.090
♪ Measuring rivers and hills,
hooves rise light ♪

35:56.230 --> 35:57.030
Didn't you guys

35:56.760 --> 35:59.340
♪ The horizon lies far ahead ♪

35:57.760 --> 35:58.670
say...

35:59.320 --> 36:00.440
We said it would be hard.

35:59.500 --> 36:01.590
♪ Swaying gently ♪

36:01.840 --> 36:03.320
But we didn't say we wouldn't go.

36:03.320 --> 36:04.280
I don't want to either.

36:03.700 --> 36:05.930
♪ Through pine mists, past 1,000 hills ♪

36:04.800 --> 36:05.920
But if my child is born

36:05.920 --> 36:07.110
and says their father is a coward,

36:05.960 --> 36:09.350
♪ Wrapped in the vast moonlight ♪

36:07.360 --> 36:08.820
I couldn't bear the shame.

36:08.840 --> 36:10.320
Without me, a First-Class Scout,

36:10.110 --> 36:12.830
♪ Having drunk the surging waves ♪

36:10.840 --> 36:12.230
can you even read a map?

36:12.710 --> 36:13.480
Commander He,

36:12.860 --> 36:15.490
♪ I care not how far the road ♪

36:13.760 --> 36:15.150
take us with you!

36:15.150 --> 36:16.920
-Take us with you!
-Take us with you!

36:16.340 --> 36:17.970
♪ Strong wine to the wild plains ♪

36:17.970 --> 36:19.780
♪ Beyond the pass,
sand blows like arrows ♪

36:19.860 --> 36:21.160
♪ I ride and whip my steed ♪

36:21.310 --> 36:23.130
♪ Chasing 10,000 miles of cloud and mist ♪

36:23.150 --> 36:24.600
♪ Mountains and rivers fade behind ♪

36:24.630 --> 36:26.630
♪ The wind crowns me ♪

36:26.650 --> 36:29.600
♪ Your eyes glow with flame ♪

36:29.640 --> 36:31.450
♪ Strong wind breaks the lute strings ♪

36:31.480 --> 36:33.320
♪ Playing for 5,000 years ♪

36:33.340 --> 36:34.850
♪ I ride my horse toward the south ♪

36:33.510 --> 36:34.150
Why?

36:34.550 --> 36:35.840
Too touched to speak?

36:34.870 --> 36:36.630
♪ Endless spring beneath my hooves ♪

36:36.550 --> 36:38.110
How about I give the order
to move out for you?

36:36.650 --> 36:38.050
♪ Hoofbeats fade away ♪

36:38.270 --> 36:39.840
♪ Rolling over peaks and ridges ♪

36:39.930 --> 36:43.140
♪ A single neigh echoes
between heaven and earth ♪

36:43.160 --> 36:45.100
♪ Treading on the clear wind ♪

36:45.230 --> 36:46.360
Listen up, the Xiuli Army!

36:46.330 --> 36:48.400
♪ The realm unfolds like a scroll ♪

36:46.630 --> 36:47.320
-Yes!
-Yes!

36:49.190 --> 36:50.670
Move out!

36:49.440 --> 36:51.440
♪ Chasing the bright moon ♪

36:50.840 --> 36:51.550
-Yes!
-Yes!

36:52.980 --> 36:56.140
♪ My spirit swallows
mountains and rivers ♪

36:59.190 --> 37:01.550
Ximeng is barren and vast,

37:01.840 --> 37:02.880
with many gaps.

37:03.510 --> 37:06.280
Now, apart from
the 20,000 Yong Army soldiers

37:06.280 --> 37:07.440
stationed outside Ximeng Pass,

37:07.440 --> 37:09.440
Zhao Che has sent 70,000 more troops

37:09.550 --> 37:11.030
to advance west in 3 routes.

37:11.030 --> 37:13.440
It seems they are heading

37:14.030 --> 37:16.190
for Xiyong Valley, Mount Kelan,

37:16.360 --> 37:18.360
and Mengshan Pass.

37:18.480 --> 37:20.190
The forces in Ximeng
are already insufficient.

37:20.190 --> 37:21.790
The Xiuli Army brought by Chu

37:22.070 --> 37:23.870
is all stationed at Ximeng Pass.

37:24.190 --> 37:26.230
The Yong Army
chose these 3 routes to attack,

37:26.230 --> 37:28.800
probably because they are remote

37:29.320 --> 37:30.550
and weakly guarded.

37:31.070 --> 37:32.030
This time,

37:32.630 --> 37:34.830
we need to gather at least 50,000 troops

37:34.960 --> 37:37.480
to help Ximeng get through this crisis.

37:37.960 --> 37:38.760
Your Majesty,

37:39.030 --> 37:41.190
for Great Yan, 50,000 troops

37:41.510 --> 37:43.190
is already all we have.

37:43.800 --> 37:45.440
After the battle at Biantang,

37:45.440 --> 37:47.960
the Black Eagle Army
has less than 20,000 left.

37:47.960 --> 37:49.030
Among these 20,000,

37:49.030 --> 37:51.280
some must stay
to guard the Capital of Great Yan.

37:51.280 --> 37:52.480
My Great Yan Army

37:52.760 --> 37:54.480
will gather immediately.

37:55.000 --> 37:57.200
Excluding those guarding the borders,

37:57.590 --> 38:00.920
I am afraid we can dispatch
10,000 men at most.

38:03.110 --> 38:03.910
Your Majesty,

38:04.360 --> 38:05.160
I understand.

38:05.710 --> 38:08.400
This battle is not only about
the survival of Ximeng,

38:08.400 --> 38:10.330
but it is also crucial to Great Yan.

38:12.880 --> 38:16.070
But right now, we are truly facing
internal and external threats.

38:16.070 --> 38:19.360
If the tribes cause trouble again

38:19.440 --> 38:20.630
while we are sending reinforcements
to Ximeng,

38:20.630 --> 38:22.890
the consequences will be unimaginable.

38:23.480 --> 38:24.280
Your Majesty.

38:27.920 --> 38:29.000
My Lady.

38:29.800 --> 38:31.460
The matter you entrusted to me

38:31.590 --> 38:33.250
has been fully investigated.

38:37.920 --> 38:39.150
As you expected,

38:39.590 --> 38:41.030
the Baichuan Tribe and the Pale Tribe,

38:41.030 --> 38:42.840
apart from the necessary garrisons,

38:42.840 --> 38:45.500
each still command
tens of thousands of troops.

38:45.510 --> 38:48.150
Together with the 6,000 cavalry
of our Helian Tribe

38:48.150 --> 38:51.480
and the 5,000 elite cavalry
you previously granted General Huan,

38:51.480 --> 38:52.340
it's precisely

38:52.670 --> 38:55.190
30,000 men.

39:11.510 --> 39:12.640
From this moment on,

39:12.760 --> 39:14.760
the Crown Prince is the new Emperor.

39:15.710 --> 39:16.510
Your Majesty,

39:17.070 --> 39:18.470
did I do it?

39:19.580 --> 39:21.580
If I refuse to stop,

39:22.510 --> 39:24.030
you will kill me,

39:24.150 --> 39:24.880
right?

39:26.000 --> 39:26.860
One hundred men

39:27.630 --> 39:28.590
is enough.

39:28.920 --> 39:31.360
Move out!

39:31.760 --> 39:32.840
-Yes!
-Yes!
